Detailed Description

Class for holding a id key for a user.

When packed into or from a packet UserIDKey looks like this. The first TYPE_ID_KEY and Total size in bytes and the last TYPE_ID_KEY is read by someone else when read from a packet. {tabular}{lll} Pos & Size & Destription \ pos & 4 bytes & TYPE_ID_KEY \ +4 & 2 bytes & Total size in bytes \ +6 & 4 bytes & TYPE_ID_KEY \ +10 & 2 bytes & Total size in bytes \ +12 & 4 bytes & ID \ +16 & 4 bytes & Type \ +20 & string & ID-Key \ {tabular}
